longBusinessSummary: O2 Secure Wireless, Inc., an Internet communications company, designs and maintains high-speed wireless broadband connection networks in the southeastern United States. The company designs, engineers, deploys, and maintains wireless broadband systems using WiFi, wireless, mobile, fixed, and consulting service technologies for residents with high-density residential communities; mobile professionals; and companies that support residential communities and mobile professionals. It also specializes in wireless tower construction and lease operations. In addition, the company's retail services include Internet, television, home phone, and mobile services; and industrial services comprise engineering, construction, build out-services, site development, and industrial consulting services. Further, it operates a retail store that offers wireless services and prepaid MasterCard cards in Palm Coast, Florida. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in Palm Coast, Florida.
